  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nAs described here, Lighthouse is returning non-standard data on `/eth/v1/node/syncing` during backfill: https://github.com/stakewise/ethnode-sidecar/issues/5\r\n\r\n## Steps to resolve\r\n\r\nI think we should exclude the backfill status from the `/eth/v1/node/syncing` endpoint. The `lighthouse/syncing` can be used instead.\r\n",
