    "body": "@michaelsproul  I can't reproduce the issue described above.\r\n\r\nFirst I analysis the code of endpoint `/eth/v1/node/syncing`, seems it won't produce the non-standard data.\r\n\r\nThen I try to reproduce in environment, the command I start client as follow:\r\n\r\n```sh\r\n### geth\r\ngeth --goerli --http --datadir /var/lib/goethereum --metrics --metrics.expensive --pprof  --authrpc.jwtsecret=/var/lib/ethereum/jwttoken --authrpc.addr localhost --authrpc.port 8551 --authrpc.vhosts localhost\r\n\r\n### lighthouse\r\nlighthouse bn \\\r\n  --network goerli  \\\r\n  --debug-level info \\\r\n  --datadir /var/lib/lighthouse \\\r\n  --http \\\r\n  --execution-endpoint http://127.0.0.1:8551 \\\r\n  --metrics \\\r\n  --validator-monitor-auto \\\r\n  --checkpoint-sync-url https://prater.checkpoint.sigp.io \\\r\n  --execution-jwt /var/lib/ethereum/jwttoken \\\r\n  --disable-deposit-contract-sync\r\n```\r\n\r\nThe version of geth and lighthouse:\r\n```sh\r\nroot@ecs-5d29:~# geth version\r\nGeth\r\nVersion: 1.11.5-unstable\r\nGit Commit: 5f81db68c6cd0544ae5f3b9b4c7b1d56d02b23da\r\nGit Commit Date: 20230313\r\nArchitecture: amd64\r\nGo Version: go1.19.3\r\nOperating System: linux\r\nGOPATH=\r\nGOROOT=\r\n\r\nroot@ecs-5d29:~# lighthouse --version\r\nLighthouse v4.0.1-9ba22b1+\r\nBLS library: blst\r\nSHA256 hardware acceleration: false\r\nAllocator: jemalloc\r\nSpecs: mainnet (true), minimal (false), gnosis (false)\r\n```\r\n\r\nI access the endpoints during backfill:\r\n\r\n```sh\r\nroot@ecs-5d29:~# curl -X GET \"http://localhost:5052/eth/v1/node/syncing\" -H  \"accept: application/json\" | jq\r\n  % Total    % Received % Xferd  Average Speed   Time    Time     Time  Current\r\n                                 Dload  Upload   Total   Spent    Left  Speed\r\n100    92  100    92    0     0   8363      0 --:--:-- --:--:-- --:--:--  8363\r\n{\r\n  \"data\": {\r\n    \"is_syncing\": false,\r\n    \"is_optimistic\": true,\r\n    \"head_slot\": \"5354534\",\r\n    \"sync_distance\": \"0\"\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\nroot@ecs-5d29:~# curl -X GET \"http://localhost:5052/lighthouse/syncing\" -H  \"accept: application/json\" | jq\r\n  % Total    % Received % Xferd  Average Speed   Time    Time     Time  Current\r\n                                 Dload  Upload   Total   Spent    Left  Speed\r\n100    67  100    67    0     0  13400      0 --:--:-- --:--:-- --:--:-- 13400\r\n{\r\n  \"data\": {\r\n    \"BackFillSyncing\": {\r\n      \"completed\": 2176,\r\n      \"remaining\": 5352128\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n```",
